{"tid":239837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴打藝團　被斥選擇性執法","createTime":"2017-05-12T02:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T03:37:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3076639629fc75407b85efedc82ff5d3a395209","tid":239837,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20018978&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20018978%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170512&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=533ca627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20018978%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170512&h=1d513459\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20018978&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170512</a><br />\n<br />\n嚴打藝團　被斥選擇性執法<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】申訴署批評食環署及地政總署疏於執法，未有檢控位於全港各工廈的違規工廠食堂，違規個案四周皆是；另一邊廂，同樣位於工廈的「Band界紅館」Hidden Agenda卻多次被政府各部門「放蛇」掃場執法，以致Hidden Agenda已多次搬遷，周日（7日）更被警方及入境處「放蛇」拒捕外國樂隊表演者及場地負責人。音樂人周博賢（圖）批評政府選擇性執法，口說重視藝術文化發展，身體欲誠實打擊有心推廣本地文化的藝團。<br />\n周博賢指，當政府對一方執法打擊，另一方卻放寬，明顯是「揀人執法」，「其實唔少藝團都長期面對打擊，不只Hidden Agenda，只係Hidden Agenda今次被高度關注」。他斥政府口說要令香港成為亞洲文化樞紐，但「得個講字」，各政府部門只一味阻礙發展。他又說，即使政府未趕得及修例，但若各部門妥善協調，藝術文化界可狹縫生存，做到林鄭月娥當初所講的「唔需要偷偷摸摸、擔驚受怕」。<br />\n■記者梁佩珊<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n公屋亂改裝　房署跟進拖3年<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n工廈食堂違規招待街客　食環地政零監管　3年僅發1口頭警告　申訴署轟卸責<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;4小時前"},{"pid":"c911d353f438ac19b3537b80a7ca9af188ca408d","tid":239837,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170512/large/a0402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170512%2Flarge%2Fa0402a.gif&h=6004b375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8aff9d24ed3c87e81fe757e5cb6ff4011114bba7","tid":239837,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾記者，寫報導咁多錯別字"}]}